{"title":"印报","authors":["罗璋"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"印报"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当人们睡得正香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你却悄悄地换上了工装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为生产精神粮食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗在这庞大的机器旁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器飞快地旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马达热情地歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报纸在你脚下翻腾着波浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你！不倦地指挥着这洪亮的大合唱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加足马力，印呀！印呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以一分钟千份的速度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把党的总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把工人、农民的经验和创造，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把祖国一日千里的建设喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把劳动的幸福和欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把你——印报工人的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全都印上！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（新湖南报工人　罗璋）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}